import React from "react";
import { Box, Center, HStack, Pressable } from "native-base";

export default function App() {
  return (
    <Center h="100vh" bg="coolGray.900">
      <Box position="relative">
        <HStack mb="3" space="3">
          <Pressable>
            {({ isHovered }) => (
              <Box
                h="150px"
                w="150px"
                postion="absolute"
                roundedTopLeft="full"
                bg="white"
                left={isHovered?"-8":"0"}
                top={isHovered?"-8":"0"}
              ></Box>
            )}
          </Pressable>
          <Box
            h="150px"
            w="150px"
            postion="absolute"
            roundedTopRight="full"
            bg="white"
          ></Box>
        </HStack>
        <HStack space="3">
          <Box
            h="150px"
            w="150px"
            postion="absolute"
            roundedBottomLeft="full"
            bg="white"
          ></Box>
          <Box
            h="150px"
            w="150px"
            postion="absolute"
            roundedBottomRight="full"
            bg="white"
          ></Box>
        </HStack>
      </Box>
    </Center>
  );
}
